plot: Snooki is bailed out of jail after her incident at the beach. JWoww continues to meet with Roger, and starts to develop feelings for him. At the club, Deena meets Ronnie's "stunt double" but realizes he's in a relationship. JWoww gets into a heated argument with Tom, thus ending their relationship. When JWoww heads to her house with Snooki, she finds that her dogs are alone and some of her things have been stolen.—Emphinix
